query:
INSERT INTO llm_cache (
	cache_id,
	cache_kind,
	cache_key,
	payload,
	created_at,
	last_accessed_at,
	expires_at,
	hit_count
)
VALUES ($1, $2, $3, $4, $5, $5, $6, 0)
ON CONFLICT (cache_kind, cache_key) DO UPDATE SET
payload = EXCLUDED.payload,
	last_accessed_at = EXCLUDED.last_accessed_at,
	expires_at = EXCLUDED.expires_at,
	hit_count = 0
